*------------------------------------------------------------------------------*
| Glass:                  ________     Limit Water Backup:       _             |
| Glass Per Pane:         ____         Water Backup:             ________      |
| Signs Not Attached:     ________     Boilers:                  _             |
| -Entirely Metal:        _                                                    |
| Signs Attached:         ________                                             |
| -Delete Ded (MCP108):   _                                                    |
| Building Code/Law:      ___                                                  |
| -ACV Basis MCP506:      _                                                    |
| Debris Removal:         ________                                             |
